{"tid":1334586,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[灣仔南地膽]  同你重點分析灣仔南走法","createTime":"2019-07-20T07:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T09:46:53.000Z","uid":12045,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"14d1bb3d9ed8db5e8e7295c2093119f4b8d1a9a6","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"細佬我係灣仔南住撚咗廿幾年，週不時通山走<br />\n跟據咁多年經驗，得出以下<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">灣仔南，向山 撤退方向</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FvANrEh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFvANrEh.png&h=c106c24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇小日月星街</span></span><br />\n正如其他巴打所言，向告士打道，沿海皮走係極危險，所以就帶大家走進灣仔以南方向 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#1 星街，星域軒 以西有條斜路，駁樓梯上堅尼地道<br />\n     星域軒以東，電氣街(姐係林保堅尼車行隔離條斜路)一樣上到堅尼地道<br />\n<br />\n#2 堅尼地道往西行(往中半山) ， 十五分鐘內 你會行經 港燈(which is 英領隔離向上行斜路，會同堅尼地道交滙)<br />\n並到達 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">紅綿路，堅道 交滙處</span>，繼續直行可以到堅道ーーー&gt;繼續往西營盤行都無問題<br />\n<br />\n#3 從堅尼地道油站起計，堅尼地道往東行，會到達 <span style=\"font-size: large;\">合和中心及皇后大道東出口</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">到達合和之前，都係直路，窄路一條。較危險</span><br />\n<br />\n#4 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">上寶雲道，會係最安全路線</span></span>，上到寶雲道，基本上係山路，行人路，入唔到車咁濟。<span style=\"color: orange;\">同時寶雲道四通八達！往西可到山頂的再往其他地方，往東可到跑馬地，往南可以去香港仔郊野公園。</span>上到寶雲道其本上一定走到！<br />\n<br />\n#5 合和以東有條樓梯，駁住堅尼地道同皇后大道東<br />\n<br />\n#6 同上，並途往樹仁分校<br />\n<br />\n#7 皇后大道東出口，一出係律頓治，華仁，st Joseph<br />\n<br />\n#8 如果係5,6 或者經合和上到堅尼地道，可行#8 灣仔峽道，跑樓梯上寶雲道。 重申一次，堅尼地道只係真路一條，比較危險。如有需要都係盡快上寶雲道撤退安全<br />\n<br />\n#9 聖嘉諾撒中學接駁皇后大道樓梯(一幻拉麵隔離上山條路) <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正在封路維修</span></span><br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"c65380d130864b0f306879a240fa8c63755be0ff","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"54e895c66dbf51247db2bc5bbd8b8eafe478910d","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:11:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a66a2285888c02daf1fe05fa7205ea7d3417443a","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:11:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c64f94b1390519d8b36b6d77cd93cc8e67c8424","tid":1334586,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:15:14.000Z","msg":"輕輕一push"},{"pid":"1ccd1c6b198e9e04599a55f29663050695090b14","tid":1334586,"uid":11322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:15:39.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"},{"pid":"9f2532fb39cfa19d0cff198f2a8725cbf600217b","tid":1334586,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"總括黎講 如果當得向南(山)同向北(海)<br />\n係咪向海危險向山相對多路線走"},{"pid":"5220d11818e3fa0f3012e2179fda174f6fc425bb","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f2532fb39cfa19d0cff198f2a8725cbf600217b","tid":1334586,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:16:52.000Z","msg":"總括黎講 如果當得向南(山)同向北(海)<br />\n係咪向海危險向山相對多路線走"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"係 你向海俾人頭尾一夾就收皮，告士打道亦都大，可以容納出動水炮車"},{"pid":"f4dcbaa6c7a253bc158f619282617e13bcdf80e8","tid":1334586,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:21:40.000Z","msg":"推爆"},{"pid":"1d69563b3332d14d4388f2976292a4b4d2af345f","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T07:22:33.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"29d5bd34059a819b46414ba06b687525a6479129","tid":1334586,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5220d11818e3fa0f3012e2179fda174f6fc425bb","tid":1334586,"uid":12045,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9f2532fb39cfa19d0cff198f2a8725cbf600217b","tid":1334586,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply